# start application
```nodemon index.js```

# all api 
  ``` post register user :- http://localhost:3000/api/register,
      get users for admin role and search and filter :- http://localhost:3000/api/users?filter=india&search=ma (search by email and name)
      require token in Authentication in that Bearer Token 
      post login user :- http://localhost:3000/api/login
      get user by id if admin then it get all user by id and if Staff then get only his own data :- http://localhost:3000/api/users/7 ```